description: These emojis are perfect for those times you need to pat someone on the head and cheer them up. It always helps to have a friend near by to offer support during times of need. Be that awesome friend who always shows up to cheer up a sad soul! Sometimes all it takes is being next to someone when they are feeling down. Send them one of these emoticons to show your support.
